Hi Everyone, I’m seeing multiple copies of some templates in the design tool appearing in the select a template stage during website-page creation and also during blog template selection in the website settings.

My guess is that they are created during deployment because I currently use a CI process to push changes to HubSpot design tools 

This duplicate files cannot be found anywhere and I don’t know how to take them out and also fix the error of multiple copies. :cold_sweat:

I would appreciate any help :raised_hands::skin-tone-3:
